import React from 'react'
import {Card, Form, Button} from 'react-bootstrap'

export default function Register(){
    return(
        <>
        <Card>style={{ width: '30rem', display: "table-cell" }}
            <Card.Img variant="top" src="/images/bookRegis.jpg" width={171} height={180} />
        </Card>
        <Card style={{ width: '30rem' }}>
            <Card.Body>
                <Card.Title>Registration Info</Card.Title>
                <Form>
                    <Form.Group controlId="nameRegis">
                        <Form.Label>Name</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Enter Full Name" />
                    </Form.Group>

                    <Form.Group controlId="unameRegis">
                        <Form.Label>Username</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Enter Username" />
                    </Form.Group>

                    <Form.Group controlId="passRegis">
                        <Form.Label>Password</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control type="password" placeholder="Enter Password" />
                    </Form.Group>

                    <Form.Group controlId="ageRegis">
                        <Form.Label>Age</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control type="number" placeholder="Enter Age" />
                    </Form.Group>
                    <Form.Group controlId="birtRegis">
                        <Form.Label>Birthday</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control type="date"/>
                    </Form.Group>
                    <Form.Group controlId="phoneRegis">
                        <Form.Label>Phone</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Enter Number Phone" />
                    </Form.Group>
                    <Form.Group controlId="addrRegis">
                        <Form.Label>Address</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Enter Address" />
                    </Form.Group>
                    <Button variant="primary" type="submit">Submit</Button>
                </Form>
            </Card.Body>
        </Card>
        </>
    );
}
